stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Normal
    Normal --> Incident: Disaster Event
    Incident --> Assessment: Trigger DRP
    Assessment --> MinorRecovery: Low Impact
    Assessment --> MajorRecovery: High Impact
    
    MinorRecovery --> Restoration: Local Recovery
    MajorRecovery --> Failover: Region Switch
    
    Restoration --> Testing: Verify Systems
    Failover --> Testing: Verify Systems
    
    Testing --> Normal: Success
    Testing --> Assessment: Failure
    
    Normal --> [*]: System Stable
